  "A lifeguard at point A on the beach needs to reach a swimmer at point B in the water. Running speed is 8 m/s on sand and swimming speed is 2 m/s. The beach point closest to B is 40 m from A and B is 30 m offshore. Where should the lifeguard enter the water to minimize travel time?": "",
  "Directly from A into the water": "",
  "Approximately 38 m from A along the beach": "",
  "Directly at the closest beach point (40 m from A)": "",
  "20 m from A": "",
